  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FiringSequence
    This class represents a firing sequence of a Petri net.
    LanguageEquivalence
    Check if two labelled transition systems accept the same prefix language.
    LanguageEquivalenceModule
    Provide the language equivalence check as a module.
    ToRegularExpressionModule
    Convert a Petri net or LTS into a language-equivalent regular expression
    Word
    This class represents a word of a formal language.
    WordInLanguage
    Check if a given word is in the prefix language of a given Petri net.
    WordInLanguageModule
    Provide the word-in-prefix-language check as a module.
    WordList
    This is a list of words.
